{"id":493703,"date":[{"year":1968,"month":12,"day":29}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"最热烈欢呼我国新的氢弹试验成功","genre":"","count":"172","ytitle":"","mtitle":"五洲高唱《东方红》","ftitle":"","authors":["万良顺"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻沪空军　万良顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红雷震得天地动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红云照得全球红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我国新的氢弹试验成功了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想显神通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想显神通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空军战士乐融融；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰昂首唱战歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利全靠毛泽东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利全靠毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰林深处笑声浓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤道战鼓擂得欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲高唱《东方红》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲高唱《东方红》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝苏修末途穷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士放眼看世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命队伍齐向东。"}]}